{"tid":996932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社署「福建計劃」下月推行　今起申請","createTime":"2019-01-26T16:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T01:07:34.000Z","uid":136705,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1fae8f385bfd340d132fc3d79184365fcb6e1664","tid":996932,"uid":136705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"社署宣布，將於4月1日推行「福建計劃」，即日起接受申請。該計劃參照「廣東計劃」安排，讓65歲或以上、選擇移居福建的香港長者，毋須每年回港亦可領取高齡津貼（現時每月1345元）。<br />\n<br />\n社署稱，「福建計劃」推行首年（本年4月1日至明年3月31日）有特別安排，讓已移居福建、但未能符合在申請日期前連續居港最少1年規定的長者，毋須先回港居住1年亦可受惠。不過，這些申請人須在申請日期前，連續在福建居住最少1年。<br />\n<br />\n查詢可瀏覽社署網頁（<a href=\"http://www.swd.gov.hk/fjs），或致電「廣東計劃」及「福建計劃」。查詢電話3105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ffjs%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E9%9B%BB%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E3%80%8D%E5%8F%8A%E3%80%8C%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E3%80%8D%E3%80%82%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B13105&d=Ew3NtGOXJSp836VkgkjnQDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=89dfee7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.swd.gov.hk/fjs），或致電「廣東計劃」及「福建計劃」。查詢電話3105</a> 3266。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以鼓勵多啲廢老返大陸住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d2cb6e0ae18528ec82701d0ec7a3dd03617d19","tid":996932,"uid":987,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"老左就要離開香港，後生就係香港打工，日日加班，到低香港咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257c8500adc7cbca93673bc9500376a3e3dd787f","tid":996932,"uid":136705,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"25d2cb6e0ae18528ec82701d0ec7a3dd03617d19","tid":996932,"uid":987,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"老左就要離開香港，後生就係香港打工，日日加班，到低香港咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"我同你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e